{"tid":2172309,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《隆重登場》大媽：播疫唔光彩","createTime":"2020-08-24T13:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T13:34:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"24820b9a01694e9f0123a9199041785a62a7471b","tid":2172309,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/KARMZI34TZEO7EKHB2IFKIJWVM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FKARMZI34TZEO7EKHB2IFKIJWVM%2F&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sbtkum%2F%2B3HP0Ta45uqRfUpIg%3D&h=5ccf3327\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FKARMZI34TZEO7EKHB2IFKIJWVM%2F&h=ca1cc2af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/KARMZI34TZEO7EKHB2IFKIJWVM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n《隆重登場》大媽：播疫唔光彩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ygw6ljnFavOEMnTMzD4rG1L6v9w=/1577x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JLEKWO4XUVHANGLLD3BEYCXH6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fygw6ljnFavOEMnTMzD4rG1L6v9w%3D%2F1577x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJLEKWO4XUVHANGLLD3BEYCXH6U.jpg&h=0ff16031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Sonia坦言沒預計晚會引致群組大爆疫，對此深感後悔。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本報調查發現，慶回歸晚宴及富臨群組均由大媽歌手群組擴散，他們並非酒廊、餐廳或商場活動的表演歌手，而是卡拉OK式的業餘歌手，為一展歌喉不但逢請必到，更不惜自費數百元或包一圍酒席，為的就是獻唱一首歌。<br />\n<br />\n據知，不少酒樓壽宴或慶祝活動，大會為搞好氣氛，主辦人都慣常邀請業餘歌手唱歌，有人更會連踩幾場，深受大會歡迎。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n坦承貼錢包枱獻唱<br />\n<br />\n憑一首《隆重登場》帶動全場的Sonia，台上多次與小雪近距離載歌載舞，事後獲悉晚會有人確診，她直言感到害怕，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n她直言當日是獲一位朋友邀請，自費320元出席，因朋友包了數圍枱，故讓她唱其中一首，無預計全場氣氛高漲，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，另一大媽歌手Sandy同場不同命，台上站在Sonia右邊狂舞的她被驗出確診，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nSandy稱原本不考慮做核酸檢測，但其除罩跳舞片流出，家人強迫她去做檢測，。。。。。。"}]}